{"tid":598091,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（玩命)外國高速滑板愛好者影片","createTime":"2018-03-19T08:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T09:53:02.000Z","uid":79181,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e77b3c4049e05246fbe8ec6e386a901d2519352b","tid":598091,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:20:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s-nBRyJyoO0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs-nBRyJyoO0&d=oK81T%2BzW%2FRBjANvf%2FMit2Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f9686018\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s-nBRyJyoO0</a><br />\n<br />\n急彎漂移<br />\n加速姿勢好似高速滑冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_bzATDSKuVs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_bzATDSKuVs&d=oK81T%2BzW%2FRBjANvf%2FMit2Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=6b8e856b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_bzATDSKuVs</a><br />\n<br />\n第二條片個景好靚，搞到好想去外國癲一次<br />\n以前睇Gopro 啲片外國好似好多依種路段比人玩<br />\n<br />\n好奇問一問<br />\n有冇玩滑板嘅巴打有試過？<br />\n想問佢地啲手套上面有塊好厚嘅野係自製還是連手套一齊訂做？<br />\n香港有冇山區路段可以咁玩？"},{"pid":"ed92566120bb85906ed3e448bfaa9518f30f337f","tid":598091,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:29:06.000Z","msg":"咁高速失平衡跌低磨薑應該會好慘<br />\n佢地只係帶頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10561f1fe3411efaeca0f7945cc427b8e9806a1","tid":598091,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af20c5e5b3cdf463838ad4586276d66c2ea7db7","tid":598091,"uid":83016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:53:13.000Z","msg":"留名等睇專業人士解答"},{"pid":"1384b81cd2094d77a12712e1bfd499eae6f1ed03","tid":598091,"uid":63,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:55:15.000Z","msg":"港柒又想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s